<section class="section" id="concluzie">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">Pe scurt</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Ce espressor automat sa cumperi – depinde de cum bei cafea</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">Trei lucruri decid: cat bei cafea pe zi, cat de mult iti pasa de <strong>spuma de lapte</strong> si cat vrei sa investesti. Iata un rezumat pe categorii de <strong>pret espressor automat</strong>.</p>

    <div class="conclusion-grid">
      <div class="conclusion-card">
        <strong>Espressor automat ieftin</strong>
        <span>De'Longhi Magnifica S sau Philips EP0824 sub 2.000 RON – rasnita integrata, cafea buna.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="conclusion-card">
        <strong>Espressor automat cappuccino</strong>
        <span>Philips EP2231 cu LatteGo sau De'Longhi Evo cu carafa – cappuccino automat in 90 secunde.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="conclusion-card">
        <strong>Cel mai bun espressor automat cafea boabe</strong>
        <span>De'Longhi Magnifica S sau Philips EP2231 – echilibru ideal pret-calitate.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="conclusion-card">
        <strong>Espressor automat profesional</strong>
        <span>Philips EP5543 seria 5500 sau Saeco GranAroma – ecran color, 16+ bauturi, profiluri multiple.</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:2rem">
      <p style="color:var(--c-text-mid);margin-bottom:1.5rem">Verifica mereu pretul actualizat pe linkurile de mai sus – se schimba des si ofertele bune dispar repede.</p>
    </div>

    <a href="/out/noutati-espressoare" class="emag-banner" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener sponsored">
      <img src="/assets/images/emag-logo.svg" alt="eMAG" class="emag-logo" width="120" height="32" />
      <span class="emag-banner-text">Vezi cele mai noi espressoare automate pe eMAG</span>
      <svg class="emag-banner-arrow" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
